## 1. **Abstract Eye (View / Inspect)**

**Use case:** Core “viewer” identity

**Prompt:**

```
A single Apple-style Liquid Glass icon asset, 1024x1024, transparent background.

Subject: a minimal abstract eye shape made of frosted glass, simplified and rounded,
with no sharp edges and no realism.

Style: Apple Human Interface Guidelines, WWDC 2025 Liquid Glass material.
Soft translucent glass, subtle internal blur, gentle rim light.
Specular highlight from the upper-left only.

Color: cool blue with slight cyan tint, restrained and calm.

Composition: centered, generous negative space, readable at small sizes.
No text, no UI, no background.
```

